[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m Alternatively, since b + 7 divides 9b + 7, then the remainder when 9b + 7 is divided by b + 7 must be zero. So, I can use the division algorithm here. Let me try to perform the division of 9b + 7 by b + 7.
