[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m ### Step 2: Use the divisibility condition
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m We can rewrite the condition $ (b + 7) \mid (9b + 7) $ by using the division algorithm:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 9b + 7 = k(b + 7)
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m for some integer $ k $. Expanding the right-hand side:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 9b + 7 = k b + 7k
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
