[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 2. **At speed $ s + 2 $**:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m    - Total time: 2 hours 24 minutes = 2.4 hours
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m    - Time spent in the coffee shop: $ t $ minutes = $ \frac{t}{60} $ hours
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m We are to find the time it takes her to walk 9 km at a speed of $ s + \frac{1}{2} $ km/h, including the $ t $ minutes spent in the coffee shop.
