[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m Bring all terms to one side:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
