[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m So:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m - $ x = \frac{60}{10} = 6 $
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m - $ x = \frac{4}{10} = 0.4 $
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m We discard $ x = 6 $ since it would make $ t = 60x = 360 $ minutes, which is not feasible in the given context. So, $ x = 0.4 $, and thus:
