[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m - $ t $ = time in minutes spent in the coffee shop.
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m - Walking time (in minutes) = total time (in minutes) - $ t $.
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m Using the formula:  
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m \text{Time} = \frac{\text{Distance}}{\text{Speed}} \times 60
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m So, for the first scenario:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m \frac{9}{s} \times 60 = 240 - t
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m \frac{540}{s} = 240 - t \tag{1}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m For the second scenario:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m \frac{9}{s + 2} \times 60 = 144 - t
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m \frac{540}{s + 2} = 144 - t \tag{2}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m ---
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m ### Step 3: Solve the System of Equations
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m From equation (1):
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m t = 240 - \frac{540}{s}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m From equation (2):
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m t = 144 - \frac{540}{s + 2}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m Set the two expressions for $ t $ equal:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 240 - \frac{540}{s} = 144 - \frac{540}{s + 2}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 96 = \frac{540}{s} - \frac{540}{s + 2}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 96 = 540 \left( \frac{1}{s} - \frac{1}{s + 2} \right)
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 96 = 540 \cdot \frac{2}{s(s + 2)} \Rightarrow 96 = \frac{1080}{s(s + 2)}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m s(s + 2) = \frac{1080}{96} = \frac{45}{4}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m Now solve the quadratic equation:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m s^2 + 2s - \frac{45}{4} = 0
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m Multiply through by 4:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 4s^2 + 8s - 45 = 0
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m Use the quadratic formula:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m s = \frac{-8 \pm \sqrt{64 + 720}}{8} = \frac{-8 \pm \sqrt{784}}{8} = \frac{-8 \pm 28}{8}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m s = \frac{20}{8} = 2.5 \quad \text{(since speed cannot be negative)}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m ---
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m ### Step 4: Find $ t $
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m Substitute $ s = 2.5 $ into equation (1):
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m t = 240 - \frac{540}{2.5} = 240 - 216 = 24 \text{ minutes}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m ---
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m ### Step 5: Find Time at $ s + \frac{1}{2} $
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m Now compute the time when she walks at $ s + \frac{1}{2} = 2.5 + 0.5 = 3 $ km/h.
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m \text{Time} = \frac{9}{3} \times 60 = 3 \times 60 = 180 \text{ minutes}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m Add the $ t = 24 $ minutes:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m \text{Total time} = 180 + 24 = 204 \text{ minutes}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m ---
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
