[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m \frac{18}{s(s + 2)} = 1.6 \Rightarrow s(s + 2) = \frac{18}{1.6} = \frac{90}{8} = 11.25
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m Now solve the quadratic equation:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m s^2 + 2s - 11.25 = 0
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m Use the quadratic formula:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m s = \frac{-2 \pm \sqrt{4 + 4 \cdot 11.25}}{2} = \frac{-2 \pm \sqrt{49}}{2} = \frac{-2 \pm 7}{2}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m So:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m s = \frac{5}{2} = 2.5 \quad \text{(since speed cannot be negative)}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m ---
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m ### Step 4: Find $ t $
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m Use the first equation:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m \frac{9}{s} + \frac{t}{60} = 4
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m Substitute $ s = 2.5 $:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m \frac{9}{2.5} + \frac{t}{60} = 4 \Rightarrow 3.6 + \frac{t}{60} = 4
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m \frac{t}{60} = 0.4 \Rightarrow t = 0.4 \cdot 60 = 24 \text{ minutes}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m ---
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m ### Step 5: Find the total time at $ s + \frac{1}{2} $ km/h
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m - New speed: $ s + \frac{1}{2} = 2.5 + 0.5 = 3 $ km/h
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m - Walking time: $ \frac{9}{3} = 3 $ hours
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m - Total time: $ 3 \text{ hours} + \frac{24}{60} \text{ hours} = 3 + 0.4 = 3.4 $ hours
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m Convert 3.4 hours to minutes:
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m 3.4 \times 60 = 204 \text{ minutes}
[36m(TaskRunner pid=202387)[0m $$
